{"tid":2265252,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"831暴動案︱相戀八年的小情侶一同被捕 今日牽手一同步出法庭：香港變得太快 好多嘢驚唔嚟","createTime":"2020-10-31T09:37:16.000Z","updateTime":"2020-11-01T15:33:40.000Z","uid":240362,"like":114,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":44,"replies":[{"pid":"b1c014fb71730e6f1e59eca2c92b7a35e56357c3","tid":2265252,"uid":240362,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:37:16.000Z","msg":"8.31灣仔暴動案中，一對相戀八年的小情侶一同被捕、一同被控，今日一同脫罪，牽手一同步出法庭。兩人一直互相扶持，經歷本案後感情更見堅固。兩人在裁決後受訪稱，坦承面對暴動罪，感到不安甚至變得懦弱，連自己開設店舖貼上的口號都移走，但仍然希望以不同方式繼續堅持。他們亦希望本案結果可為日後的暴動被告在選擇答辯方向時，帶來參考與幫助。<br />\n<br />\n同為24歲的余德穎及莫嘉晴一同受訪。莫嘉晴稱昨晚難以入睡，「好想把握最後嘅時間咁，喺度碌電話上網，唔捨得瞓」。男友余德穎在旁補充，「肉體上好攰，但瞓唔到。你唔知離開咗屋企，之後幾耐先可以返去」，並說昨晚不斷「聞貓」，把握相處時間。他又指兩人已很久沒有談過電話，「昨日竟然講咗次電話」。<br />\n<br />\n余回憶，起初不知控方有何證據，直至開審前一星期才得悉，「見到警察對我嘅指控，全部都係假嘅、生安白造，你就覺得全部係為咗鋤死你而作出呢啲證據」。他一直擔心法官或會接納警員證供。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/Z3KVBTKSWZFUVGKFG7EVZWTOVI/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FZ3KVBTKSWZFUVGKFG7EVZWTOVI%2F&d=DHxvyfXarR7adKHN0Usak3vcSryOYOd41eK7VOq09cM%3D&h=4bd81467\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201031%2FZ3KVBTKSWZFUVGKFG7EVZWTOVI%2F&h=961b1723\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201031/Z3KVBTKSWZFUVGKFG7EVZWTOVI/</a>"},{"pid":"f01110565b4cc17e6b4c463fd8f84df4d82f51cc","tid":2265252,"uid":103965,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:37:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cat/rain.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"46fb684bb6062f10ec158ccf9ff63d666aceb164","tid":2265252,"uid":14211,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:37:49.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"93c6b318ee67116f0d33d3893f396804065ac183","tid":2265252,"uid":27122,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:37:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03313119a0fc535681687eb183d3dbe84c8fa172","tid":2265252,"uid":240362,"like":26,"dislike":0,"score":26,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:38:14.000Z","msg":"<strong><span class=\"red\">兩人自中學起相戀，本來曾談論結婚，但莫嘉晴自言捲入暴動案後，「人生好似停頓咗咁，冇可能有任何規劃，唔可以搵一份長工、唔會去報上堂。就算係想買個iPhone都唔會買，可能只係用三個月。依家都唔會諗結婚，我會想喺安穩嘅日子結囉，我唔想結完婚之後分開六年」。<br />\n<br />\n莫是一名社工，現時開網店賣潮牌衣服，「訂唔訂貨都決定唔到，每一日都係見步行步」，本來更打算一旦入獄便讓媽媽打理網店。</span></strong>"},{"pid":"9baf950dbde865b31be804b65dbda05126ad289b","tid":2265252,"uid":96327,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:38:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a9a6c2a77f453c907fe2ad5f2c0f029daa6f7746","tid":2265252,"uid":55089,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:38:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8f25e973d8db878c9e025aebaff8694e7554d5d0","tid":2265252,"uid":51271,"like":0,"dislike":10,"score":-10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:38:49.000Z","msg":"全部都係假既"},{"pid":"bd60c47126673428126614788bf5a8ee1c35e698","tid":2265252,"uid":79117,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-31T09:39:16.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"11dc06f6ee247bb45c76ff7ee40db10d7c0dc6f5","tid":2265252,"uid":